==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lanch
<hw>Lanch</hw> <pr>(l⟦adot⟧nch)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Lanched</conjf>
<pr>(l⟦adot⟧ncht)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Lanching</conjf>. See <er>Launch</er>, <er>Lance</er>.]</vmorph>
<def>To throw, as a lance; to let fly; to launch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>See Whose arm can <qex>lanch</qex> the surer bolt.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden & Lee.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lanciferous</ent>⟦br⟧
